The paper discusses the application of machine learning to computer architecture design, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on system-wide simulation and optimization, which could be categorized under Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses specific components such as memory systems, branch predictors, networks-on-chip, and GPUs, which could be categorized under Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper mentions the use of neural networks, which falls under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
